Did you prepare the conference room?

06:09.176 --> 06:10.871
<i>Yeah. PowerPoint's all set up,
nobody knows a thing.</i>

06:11.345 --> 06:14.007
<i>Okay. Well, get out of here.</i>

06:15.615 --> 06:17.549
Everyone here is familiar with Dr. Sinja.

06:17.951 --> 06:19.543
