07:17.911 --> 07:19.811
<i>- God!
- All right, all right, Jack.</i>

07:19.880 --> 07:22.280
<i>Assuming you can actually
get an audience with the guy,</i>

07:22.349 --> 07:24.476
you're not the only agent in town
