08:27.547 --> 08:30.038
Your face
before your parents were born.

08:30.517 --> 08:32.144
"Your face
before your parents were born"?

08:32.219 --> 08:34.482
That's a great title for a kids' show.

08:34.554 --> 08:35.782
It has many names.

08:36.823 --> 08:40.657
<i>Nirvana, kensho, bliss,</i>

08:41.126 --> 08:44.824
<i>divinity, illumination.
Let's call it the Blue Pearl.</i>

08:47.300 --> 08:50.269
It's okay. Our truth can be painful.

08:51.204 --> 08:53.104
Pain is the touchstone of growth.

08:54.341 --> 08:56.502
