Students meditate for years

09:29.243 --> 09:31.871
and never see
what you have seen today.

09:31.946 --> 09:33.607
Your inner self.

09:33.681 --> 09:36.013
<i>That makes you
a very special person, Mr...</i>

09:36.083 --> 09:37.107
McCall.

09:37.485 --> 09:39.282
Jack McCall. Thank you so much.

09:45.560 --> 09:46.549
<i>Sorry, I don't know what happened.</i>

09:46.627 --> 09:48.424
I just got overcome with emotion.
I'm sorry.

09:48.496 --> 09:49.793
My years and years of focused silence

09:49.931 --> 09:52.923
just finally delivered me to...

09:53.000 --> 09:55.400
