- Enlightenment, yes. Enlightenment.</i>

09:57.104 --> 09:58.731
Sorry. Hold that a second.

09:59.040 --> 10:02.168
I'm so sorry.
Play it four times and it stops.

10:12.186 --> 10:13.380
