"and the truth. "

10:34.875 --> 10:37.503
<i>Is there a reason for your visit today,
Jack McCall?</i>

10:37.578 --> 10:39.739
<i>Well, sir, I am not one to waste time.</i>

10:39.814 --> 10:40.872
I understand you've written a book.

10:41.649 --> 10:42.638
That is true.

10:42.717 --> 10:45.242
<i>Well, I'm an agent.</i>

10:45.319 --> 10:47.446
And all my career
I've dreamed that I'd get to represent

10:47.521 --> 10:49.989
