I believe in you.

10:50.825 --> 10:53.726
And I think
I can help you to change the world.

10:55.730 --> 10:56.754
I'm not interested.

10:59.266 --> 11:00.255
Really?

11:01.369 --> 11:03.200
<i>Dr. Sinja? Dr. Sinja, the world</i>

11:03.437 --> 11:07.203
