11:18.653 --> 11:21.121
<i>Trees, I love them. I love trees.</i>

11:21.188 --> 11:23.679
The branches and the leaves. It's just...

11:23.758 --> 11:25.191
<i>You know,
some people want fame and money.</i>

11:25.259 --> 11:28.023
<i>Just give me some nature,
some branches and some trees.</i>

11:28.095 --> 11:29.084
I love it.

11:29.930 --> 11:31.488
<i>In fact,
I have such an affinity towards trees</i>

11:31.565 --> 11:33.328
