11:34.001 --> 11:36.367
Just...

11:37.705 --> 11:40.606
Landing on a branch. Taking it all in.

11:41.676 --> 11:45.442
I want to be a bird. I want to be a bird
and I want to swallow your philosophy.

11:45.513 --> 11:46.810
And then I'm gonna spit it back
into the mouths

11:46.881 --> 11:47.870
of the children of the world.

11:48.749 --> 11:52.048
<i>Nourish their souls. Help you to grow,
watch your wings spread,</i>

11:52.486 --> 11:53.976
and help you to soar.

11:54.989 --> 11:56.047
What are you talking about?

11:57.058 --> 12:00.152
