12:29.256 --> 12:31.554
<i>Mind, body and spirit. Everything.</i>

12:33.694 --> 12:35.491
Let me be a big bird.

12:36.030 --> 12:37.190
Hawk!

12:37.932 --> 12:39.957
Or sparrow.

12:40.034 --> 12:41.433
