in the way I meant it to be spread?

12:51.512 --> 12:53.241
<i>That goes without saying.
You have my word, sir.</i>

12:56.383 --> 12:58.874
<i>Remember, our words have a profound</i>

12:58.953 --> 13:01.217
rippling effect on the entire universe.

13:01.288 --> 13:03.381
<i>Well, I'm counting on that.</i>

13:04.625 --> 13:05.887
<i>- Jack McCall's office.
- Aaron!</i>

13:06.026 --> 13:07.755
<i>I want you to run out
and buy me a throne,</i>

13:07.828 --> 13:10.422
<i>and a scepter and a crown,
because I am the king!</i>

13:11.265 --> 13:13.256
<i>Oh, my God, Mr. McCall.
You signed him, didn't you?</i>

13:13.334 --> 13:15.234
You bet your ass I signed him.

13:15.302 --> 13:17.133
Never doubt me! Never doubt me!

13:17.338 --> 13:18.327
<i>How about that?</i>

13:18.405 --> 13:20.236
<i>Hey, I want you to clear
