14:12.059 --> 14:13.390
<i>Yeah, he was. He's dead now.</i>

14:13.460 --> 14:15.360
- I'm sorry.
- I'm not.

14:15.663 --> 14:17.528
You sure she should be drinking
these margaritas?

14:17.598 --> 14:18.860
Don't worry.

14:18.933 --> 14:21.527
<i>'Cause unlike me,
these margaritas are virgins.</i>

14:23.037 --> 14:25.005
