14:29.076 --> 14:32.045
It's like you're smuggling walnuts
in a polyester purse!

14:32.112 --> 14:33.602
<i>Okay, all right.</i>

14:33.681 --> 14:37.048
Tonight it's fajitas
and taquitos with fresh guacamole.

14:37.117 --> 14:38.675
<i>Oh, gracias, Tim.</i>

14:39.787 --> 14:42.085
<i>How you doin', Mom? You okay?</i>

14:42.156 --> 14:45.489
Look at that suit.
You look like a gangster.

14:47.361 --> 14:49.387
Why don't you wear
that suit we got married in?

14:49.898 --> 14:51.729
<i>Because I'm Jack, your son, Ma,</i>

14:51.800 --> 14:54.132
and I got to wear clothes like this
because I need it for my work.

14:54.202 --> 14:56.966
<i>I'm a big agent, remember?
Hey, I made a big deal today.</i>

14:57.739 --> 14:58.831
Jack?

14:59.541 --> 15:03.500
<i>Raymond,
Jack never forgave you for leaving.</i>

15:03.578 --> 15:06.069
- Ma!
- And Jack missed my birthday again.

15:06.147 --> 15:08.911
<i>Mom, I'm Jack. I'm your son. I'm here!</i>

15:10.385 --> 15:11.477
What?

15:17.292 --> 15:18.316
<i>Happy birthday, Mom.</i>

15:20.362 --> 15:22.330
And Caroline says hello.

15:30.572 --> 15:32.096
<i>Raymond,</i>

15:32.173 --> 15:33.970
is that you?

15:35.810 --> 15:38.176
<i>No, Ma. It's me, Jack. Your son.</i>

15:41.750 --> 15:45.186
<i>I'm going to get going now
and get back to work, so...</i>

15:49.291 --> 15:50.553
Love you.

16:00.402 --> 16:02.336
<i>Hola, Gaudencio. You're here late, huh?</i>

16:02.404 --> 16:06.898
<i>Hi, Mr. McCall.
The sprinkler, it die, but I fix it.</i>

16:10.612 --> 16:12.671
Okay.

16:12.747 --> 16:15.648
<i>This is it. It's a beautiful house, Jack.</i>

16:16.451 --> 16:17.884
The neighborhood is so sweet.

16:17.953 --> 16:19.420
There are kids everywhere.

16:19.487 --> 16:20.511
<i>While I was there,</i>

16:20.588 --> 16:23.284
an ice cream truck
actually came through.

16:23.358 --> 16:25.417
<i>I mean, it's just...</i>

16:26.227 --> 16:27.888
It's perfect for us.

16:28.430 --> 16:30.022
But this house is perfect for us.

16:30.532 --> 16:32.056
We made Tyler in this house.

16:32.133 --> 16:33.430
We made Tyler in this room.

16:33.501 --> 16:36.026
We made Tyler on this table. Tyler...

16:36.104 --> 16:40.734
<i>Okay. If we're going to stay
in this house, which I'm willing to do,</i>

16:40.809 --> 16:42.606
we have to do some work
to make it safer.

16:42.978 --> 16:44.502
More family friendly.

16:44.579 --> 16:46.706
What are you talking about?
This place is perfectly safe.

16:46.781 --> 16:50.217
<i>No. Look, just beyond
these polished concrete floors</i>

16:50.285 --> 16:51.843
is a non-fenced pool

16:52.287 --> 16:56.121
<i>that backs up to a cliff
with a sheer drop of 2,000 feet.</i>

16:58.893 --> 17:00.326
<i>Well, look,
maybe we should let the kid grow up</i>

17:00.395 --> 17:02.329
and tell us where he wants to live.

17:02.397 --> 17:04.387
It's a bachelor pad!

17:04.465 --> 17:05.454
He's a bachelor!

17:05.532 --> 17:08.434
Okay.
We cannot raise a family in this house.

17:08.502 --> 17:10.528
<i>Hey, look,
I bought this house on my potential</i>

17:10.605 --> 17:11.970
and then I earned it. I love this house.

17:12.040 --> 17:15.531
<i>I love it, too,
but I'm changing Tyler at the bar.</i>

17:16.444 --> 17:18.002
He sleeps in your media room.

17:18.113 --> 17:20.637
It's like we're guests in your house.

17:21.082 --> 17:22.777
It's just time.

17:24.019 --> 17:26.419
<i>You know, moving is a huge change.</i>

17:26.488 --> 17:30.754
<i>I know, but so was getting married,</i>

17:30.825 --> 17:32.622
and having a baby.

17:32.694 --> 17:36.130
<i>And those turned out
to be really nice changes, right?</i>

17:41.069 --> 17:42.058
<i>Okay, let's do it.</i>

17:42.704 --> 17:43.898
Really?

17:45.740 --> 17:47.640
Let's paint the media room.

17:48.176 --> 17:51.543
<i>Yeah, let's put some ducks in there
and some cartoon figures</i>

17:51.613 --> 17:53.240
<i>and, you know,
just keep it mid-century modern, though.</i>

17:53.314 --> 17:54.303
Mid-century modern ducks.

17:54.382 --> 17:56.179
<i>- Yeah, mid-century modern and ducks.
- That's fantastic.</i>

17:56.251 --> 17:57.513
That actually sounds kinda hot.

17:57.685 --> 18:00.415
<i>An all new low for you, Jack.</i>

18:00.488 --> 18:02.513
<i>- Hey, now what are you doing?
- I'm cleaning up.</i>

18:11.266 --> 18:13.393
- What the hell was that?
- An earthquake?

18:13.601 --> 18:16.502
I've been in an earthquake.
That wasn't an earthquake.

18:17.072 --> 18:18.733
I'm gonna check on Tyler!

18:42.397 --> 18:44.888
<i>This is a beautiful tree, my friend.</i>

18:44.966 --> 18:46.433
<i>Please, tell me
why you would plant a tree</i>

18:46.501 --> 18:47.900
right in the middle of the patio.

18:47.969 --> 18:49.368
I no plant the tree.

18:49.437 --> 18:50.734
You no plant the tree?

18:50.805 --> 18:53.171
I've been here all day
fixing the sprinkler.

18:53.241 --> 18:54.902
I coming back to pick up my things

18:54.976 --> 18:56.967
<i>and, boom, it's a tree here.</i>

18:57.045 --> 18:58.376
<i>"Boom, it's a tree here"?</i>

18:58.446 --> 18:59.538
Boom.

19:02.350 --> 19:04.818
<i>Hey, this is that tree that bit me.</i>

19:06.254 --> 19:07.619
Why the hell would he send me
something like this?

19:07.689 --> 19:09.884
<i>What, is this a joke or something?</i>

19:09.958 --> 19:10.947
He must think it's a gift.

19:12.193 --> 19:14.593
<i>Well, now I'm stuck
with this goddamned thing?</i>

19:14.662 --> 19:17.495
<i>I was gonna just send him a nice wine
or, you know,</i>

19:17.565 --> 19:19.260
a Harry and David's Fruit of the Month.

19:19.334 --> 19:22.963
Or a massage. Or Mrs. Fields cookies.

19:23.037 --> 19:25.062
Exactly.

19:25.140 --> 19:26.903
You want me to get rid of it?

19:26.975 --> 19:30.809
<i>No, I gotta make nice.
I'll keep it. This is my tree now.</i>

19:31.946 --> 19:35.712
<i>- Okay, Mr. McCall. See you mañana.
- Thanks.</i>

19:41.055 --> 19:42.454
Sorta classy.

19:56.504 --> 19:57.732
<i>- Mr. McCall?
- Faster, Aaron.</i>

19:57.805 --> 19:59.898
<i>Please, be less dumb,
but be quicker about it.</i>

19:59.974 --> 20:01.635
I got a splitting headache today.

20:01.709 --> 20:02.698
Are you sick?

20:02.777 --> 20:05.143
<i>No, I think I'm having
an allergic reaction or something.</i>

20:05.213 --> 20:08.580
<i>Well, this should cheer you up.
Here's your crown.</i>

20:08.650 --> 20:09.912
And the throne's on order.

20:09.984 --> 20:12.817
<i>But they offered me a scepter,
so I bought it.</i>

20:14.689 --> 20:15.781
Are you a moron?

20:16.558 --> 20:17.547
No.

20:18.459 --> 20:21.121
<i>So Sinja sent his book over, and...</i>

20:21.196 --> 20:22.595
- How great is it?
- You read it?

20:23.331 --> 20:24.525
How many times
do we have to go through this?

20:24.599 --> 20:25.793
I don't read!

20:25.867 --> 20:27.164
<i>Once again, how was Sinja's book?</i>

20:27.235 --> 20:28.759
<i>No, let me tell you.
It was scintillating, huh?</i>

20:28.836 --> 20:30.770
<i>You couldn't stop reading it, just like it
was your latest copy</i>

20:30.838 --> 20:31.863
<i>of Juggs magazine, right?</i>

20:32.308 --> 20:34.503
<i>It is a quick read, that's fair.</i>

20:34.577 --> 20:35.839
<i>Way to go, Sinja!</i>

20:35.911 --> 20:38.106
It's almost like the book was written
for you.

20:38.180 --> 20:39.807
<i>Of course it was! Listen, this book is...</i>

20:39.882 --> 20:41.474
Five pages long.

20:46.488 --> 20:48.046
Five pages long?

20:48.123 --> 20:49.715
Five pages long.

20:50.793 --> 20:52.226
<i>As in one, two, three, four...</i>

20:52.294 --> 20:53.989
Five. The end.

20:55.397 --> 20:57.194
But look at it this way.
It's the perfect book for you

20:57.266 --> 20:58.563
because the first five pages

20:58.634 --> 21:01.330
and the last five pages
are the whole book.

21:02.438 --> 21:03.564
<i>Okay, Aaron, come on.</i>

21:03.639 --> 21:05.266
<i>Tell me that you're pulling my pecker
on this one, right?</i>

21:05.441 --> 21:07.466
<i>Oh, I wish I could.</i>

21:07.543 --> 21:08.874
<i>I mean, not your pecker, but...</i>

21:09.645 --> 21:10.634
Let me see it.

21:11.847 --> 21:13.644
- My...
- The book!

21:18.053 --> 21:19.077
No.

21:19.989 --> 21:22.423
- That's the book?
- That's the book.

21:30.532 --> 21:32.727
<i>Okay. Okay,
I'm gonna go down to that ashram</i>

21:32.801 --> 21:34.603
and I'm gonna ram this up his ass!

21:34.770 --> 21:36.032
<i>It's just the dedication, right?</i>

21:36.105 --> 21:38.835
Or the teaser? Or the thank you's.

21:38.907 --> 21:41.774
<i>Jack, you said you loved my book.</i>

21:41.844 --> 21:43.835
<i>That wasn't a book you gave me,
it was a pamphlet!</i>

21:43.912 --> 21:45.243
I've read menus that were longer!

21:45.314 --> 21:47.407
I read a stop sign on the way here
that was longer than that!

21:47.483 --> 21:51.817
<i>Now, my book
is a journey of self-discovery.</i>

21:51.887 --> 21:54.947
<i>Now, that journey is fulfilled
by page five.</i>

21:55.024 --> 21:56.116
<i>Okay, it's coming together now.</i>

21:56.191 --> 21:57.556
<i>You know, you got
a lot of tricks up your sleeve.</i>

21:57.626 --> 22:00.493
<i>First, the magic tree.
Then the book with five pages.</i>

22:00.562 --> 22:02.223
What's next?
You gonna get on a magic yoga mat

22:02.298 --> 22:03.492
and fly around in a circle?

22:03.565 --> 22:05.328
<i>Then you rub your stomach,
but then, whoosh,</i>

22:05.401 --> 22:07.301
the genie jumps out of my ass?

22:09.138 --> 22:11.333
<i>Bless you, Jack. Are you okay?</i>

22:11.407 --> 22:13.068
I'm having an allergic reaction.

22:13.142 --> 22:14.939
It's probably from that tree you sent me.

22:15.444 --> 22:17.105
I sent you a tree?

22:18.013 --> 22:19.139
See?

22:19.982 --> 22:22.712
So this is where the tree went.

22:23.552 --> 22:24.644
What?

22:25.254 --> 22:26.278
Interesting.

22:27.556 --> 22:29.387
What's so interesting?

22:29.658 --> 22:31.785
These branches
don't have a single leaf.

22:32.428 --> 22:33.759
<i>You know, I noticed that, too.</i>

22:39.335 --> 22:40.324
Jack?

22:42.137 --> 22:44.628
Look at the tree and say something.

22:47.676 --> 22:48.665
Say what?

22:53.682 --> 22:54.842
What's so funny?

22:55.617 --> 22:57.585
This is amazing. Don't you see?

23:00.089 --> 23:02.683
<i>Hey, you know, it almost seems
like every time I say something,</i>

23:02.758 --> 23:04.248
some of the...

23:13.902 --> 23:15.062
Hello?

23:20.542 --> 23:21.600
Hel...

23:23.245 --> 23:24.303
...lo!

23:29.284 --> 23:30.774
<i>I want my baby back
baby back, baby back</i>

23:30.853 --> 23:32.844
<i>I want my baby back, baby back ribs</i>

23:34.990 --> 23:36.082
Shit!

23:37.526 --> 23:39.050
<i>Hey, how are you doing this?</i>

23:39.128 --> 23:40.993
Me? I'm doing nothing.

23:42.097 --> 23:44.361
You and this tree are now connected.

23:44.433 --> 23:45.900
Connected?

23:47.469 --> 23:49.733
It seems like
all your talking is making you sick.

23:49.972 --> 23:51.439
<i>Hey, my talking is not making me sick.</i>

23:52.608 --> 23:57.545
<i>Oh, really? What happens
when a tree loses all its leaves, Jack?</i>

23:57.613 --> 23:58.807
<i>So what are you trying to say, Sinja?</i>

23:59.348 --> 24:01.578
<i>It's obvious to me, the more you talk,</i>

24:01.650 --> 24:03.743
<i>the more leaves fall, the sicker you get.</i>

24:04.219 --> 24:05.516
The sicker I get?

24:05.587 --> 24:07.316
So what happens
if all the leaves fall off the tree?

24:08.791 --> 24:10.759
That usually means the tree is dead.

24:11.527 --> 24:12.824
<i>Hey, wait a second. Hold on a second.</i>

24:12.895 --> 24:14.055
You telling me that you think

24:14.129 --> 24:16.120
whatever happens to the tree
happens to me?

24:16.198 --> 24:17.187
Yes.

24:18.801 --> 24:20.530
So I could die!

24:20.602 --> 24:24.060
<i>Yes, but you would die
in the most amazing way possible.</i>

24:24.339 --> 24:25.829
I could die?

24:25.908 --> 24:28.502
Or someone could turn you
into a coffee table.

24:28.577 --> 24:30.340
<i>Hey, Sinja, you know,
you're a real funny dude to stand here</i>

24:30.412 --> 24:33.438
making jokes when my life
is being controlled by this magic tree!

24:34.249 --> 24:36.274
How many leaves
you think are left on this tree?

24:37.152 --> 24:38.517
A thousand?

24:39.354 --> 24:40.912
<i>So what do I got, a thousand words left?</i>

24:42.324 --> 24:44.417
Now you have 993.

24:45.494 --> 24:47.223
<i>One word, one leaf.</i>

24:50.999 --> 24:53.627
<i>Well, I know how to make this shit stop.</i>

24:57.306 --> 24:58.773
<i>Oh, no, no, you shouldn't do this.</i>

24:59.174 --> 25:01.108
<i>- That is murder!
- Yeah, and it's premeditated, too!</i>

25:01.176 --> 25:02.666
<i>Jack, you shouldn't do this!</i>

25:02.744 --> 25:05.304
<i>You know what, Sinja?
You worry about pages six through 200</i>

25:05.380 --> 25:07.507
and you let me worry
about Mr. Tricky Tree over here!

25:07.583 --> 25:09.983
<i>And on that note, one last final word!</i>

25:10.052 --> 25:11.519
Timber!

25:21.697 --> 25:23.756
Be glad you don't own a chainsaw.

25:25.000 --> 25:26.024
Why did you do this to me?

25:26.101 --> 25:28.194
I didn't do this. I wouldn't know how.

25:28.270 --> 25:29.703
<i>So, what, the universe cursed me?</i>

25:29.771 --> 25:33.468
Maybe.
This is between you and the tree.

25:33.542 --> 25:36.443
<i>Hey, wait a minute. If this is real,
what am I supposed to do?</i>

25:36.512 --> 25:38.537
You ever heard of this before?
You ever seen anything like this?

25:38.981 --> 25:40.141
<i>I've never seen it,</i>

25:40.215 --> 25:42.911
but there is a story
of an old monk that had a tree like this.

25:42.985 --> 25:45.112
I always thought it was just a story.

25:45.187 --> 25:47.087
He became very famous and honored.

25:47.456 --> 25:48.445
So he lived.

25:48.524 --> 25:50.014
<i>No, he died.</i>

25:50.092 --> 25:51.116
Jesus.

25:51.193 --> 25:53.957
<i>No, his name was Stan.</i>

25:54.029 --> 25:55.690
I'm leaving for Bolivia tonight.

25:55.764 --> 25:58.324
A spiritual retreat
in Potosí called La Paz.

25:58.400 --> 26:01.198
Let me talk to my colleagues there
about you and your tree.

26:01.270 --> 26:02.862
<i>Bolivia? Well, when you coming back?</i>

26:03.438 --> 26:04.666
- In three days.
- Three days?

26:04.740 --> 26:06.173
What am I supposed to do until then?

26:06.241 --> 26:08.209
<i>If I were you, Jack, I'd be quiet.</i>

26:08.577 --> 26:11.569
Don't talk for three days.
How hard can it be?

26:17.353 --> 26:18.377
Hello!

26:20.790 --> 26:21.779
Shit.

26:23.326 --> 26:24.452
<i>Come on, Jack.</i>

26:24.694 --> 26:26.889
What is the purpose
in cursing you with a tree

26:26.963 --> 26:30.490
that loses a leaf
with every word you speak?

26:30.567 --> 26:32.467
That is ridiculous!

26:35.538 --> 26:37.335
I guess you're right.

26:39.342 --> 26:40.366
It's crazy!

26:40.443 --> 26:42.104
It's ridiculous!

26:48.418 --> 26:49.476
Did you see that?

26:49.552 --> 26:50.780
See what?

26:50.853 --> 26:54.289
<i>A leaf with every word!
Jack, you slay me!</i>

26:56.593 --> 26:58.618
<i>Oh, Lord Jesus!
God, oh, God, oh, God, oh, my God!</i>

26:58.695 --> 27:01.425
<i>God, oh, God, oh, God,
oh, God, oh, God!</i>

27:18.047 --> 27:19.275
Morning.

28:16.272 --> 28:19.764
<i>Good morning, sir.
What can I get started for you today?</i>

28:21.377 --> 28:22.708
What size?

28:23.846 --> 28:25.814
<i>All right, three venti lattes.</i>

28:26.449 --> 28:29.145
Would you care for a pastry? No?

28:31.721 --> 28:33.985
<i>Oh, mocha! Three mocha lattes.</i>

28:37.060 --> 28:40.154
Double chocolate-chip muffin! Yum!

28:45.968 --> 28:48.698
You want three Paul McCartney CDs.
Awesome.

28:49.005 --> 28:52.372
<i>You know, I love the Beatles.
They are my life.</i>

28:57.413 --> 28:59.142
Assassination! Abraham Lincoln!

29:00.516 --> 29:04.008
<i>You, me, gun, shoot!</i>

29:06.022 --> 29:07.011
Three shots.

29:08.791 --> 29:10.986
<i>I know, I'm a little slow today.</i>

29:12.228 --> 29:15.755
<i>All right, so three lattes, three mochas,</i>

29:15.832 --> 29:18.460
double chocolate-chip muffin
and three shots.

29:18.701 --> 29:20.828
No assassinations.

29:20.903 --> 29:23.064
And three Paul McCartney CDs.

29:23.940 --> 29:25.464
That's gonna be $68.12.

29:38.588 --> 29:40.852
Could you tell me when
it's safe to cross?

29:42.892 --> 29:45.156
<i>Are you deaf? I said,</i>

29:45.661 --> 29:48.528
"Can you tell me
when it's safe to cross?"

29:50.767 --> 29:52.632
<i>It is? Thanks, fella!</i>

30:00.810 --> 30:02.243
<i>Stop it, stop it, stop it!</i>

30:11.988 --> 30:14.980
<i>Hey, my brother, what's happening,
brother? What's going on?</i>

30:15.825 --> 30:17.520
Hey! Was that a drive-by?
What was that?

30:17.593 --> 30:18.992
<i>Somebody tell me, was that a drive-by?</i>

30:23.599 --> 30:25.726
<i>Thanks, son! White people sure is nice!</i>

30:56.999 --> 30:58.125
<i>Hey, Mr. McCall.</i>

30:58.367 --> 31:01.063
<i>Hey, about my book,
any chance you read it yet?</i>

31:01.137 --> 31:03.469
<i>Great story, right?</i>

31:03.539 --> 31:07.305
<i>Oh, you did read it.
Oh, God, and you hate the story.</i>

31:07.977 --> 31:09.274
<i>Okay, but the writing is good, right?</i>

31:10.646 --> 31:13.012
<i>No? Well, why don't you lie to me?</i>

31:13.082 --> 31:15.448
You've been lying to me for three years
about how you couldn't read it.

31:15.518 --> 31:16.576
<i>Now suddenly you read it, you hate it,</i>

31:16.652 --> 31:18.415
it sucks and you just smash my hopes

31:18.487 --> 31:20.614
<i>on the rocks of
"Hey, Wayne, go back to Nebraska</i>

31:20.690 --> 31:21.782
"and shave sheep with your dad. "

31:22.458 --> 31:25.484
You don't know what it's like
to be a writer. I hate myself.

31:25.561 --> 31:28.359
<i>I hate myself, do you get that?
I hate myself!</i>

31:34.470 --> 31:36.836
I'll park your car.

31:36.906 --> 31:39.204
<i>Yeah, I'll park your car,
Mr. Encouragement.</i>

31:39.342 --> 31:40.639
<i>Mr. McCall, thank God you're here.</i>

31:40.710 --> 31:42.371
I have a lot of messages.

31:42.445 --> 31:44.310
Do you want to start with the most
recent or the most urgent?

31:44.647 --> 31:46.046
<i>You got a sore throat? Okay, don't talk.</i>

31:47.650 --> 31:50.141
Okay. How about some tea?

31:50.219 --> 31:53.086
Cough medicine?
How about a notepad to write on?

31:55.258 --> 31:56.748
Okay.

31:56.826 --> 32:00.524
<i>Well, then how am I supposed to know
what you want me to...</i>

32:01.765 --> 32:04.495
