01:08:28.721 --> 01:08:31.850
<i>You never think you got
Bad luck, bad luck</i>

01:08:31.926 --> 01:08:32.915
Stop talking!

01:08:50.678 --> 01:08:52.167
<i>Oh, thank God.</i>

01:08:58.886 --> 01:08:59.875
Caroline.

01:09:18.439 --> 01:09:22.033
There's really nothing in college
that prepares you

01:09:22.109 --> 01:09:24.134
to work in the real world.

01:10:54.835 --> 01:10:57.702
<i>Tree, can you hear me?</i>

01:10:59.139 --> 01:11:00.231
<i>Tree.</i>

01:11:02.142 --> 01:11:03.803
<i>We're dying, tree.</i>

01:11:06.480 --> 01:11:08.573
<i>Please, tell me what to do.</i>

01:11:09.149 --> 01:11:10.377
<i>It's me.</i>

01:11:11.752 --> 01:11:13.652
<i>My name is Jack McCall.</i>

01:11:14.955 --> 01:11:16.217
<i>If you can hear me,</i>

01:11:16.290 --> 01:11:19.748
<i>what you're listening to
is not the sound of my voice.</i>

01:11:19.827 --> 01:11:23.388
<i>It's the sound of my inner voice,
the one inside my head.</i>

01:11:33.507 --> 01:11:35.168
<i>Mr. McCall?</i>

01:11:35.509 --> 01:11:36.533
<i>Hello?</i>

01:11:37.411 --> 01:11:41.108
Can you hear me?
It's Emily from the nursing home.

01:11:41.915 --> 01:11:45.646
<i>It's your mom's birthday
and she expects Raymond to be here.</i>

01:11:45.853 --> 01:11:46.911
<i>Mr. McCall?</i>

01:12:37.172 --> 01:12:38.264
Look.

01:12:39.040 --> 01:12:40.064
<i>I know what you want,</i>

01:12:40.141 --> 01:12:42.541
<i>but I just don't think that there's anything
more to talk about, okay?</i>

01:12:42.610 --> 01:12:44.168
Because you won't...

01:12:49.150 --> 01:12:50.208
You.

01:12:51.686 --> 01:12:52.710
Me.

01:12:55.590 --> 01:12:56.614
We.

01:12:58.526 --> 01:12:59.788
Eternity.

01:13:21.716 --> 01:13:23.047
Is this for me?

01:13:24.686 --> 01:13:26.551
It's a Beatles record.

01:13:28.289 --> 01:13:29.950
<i>It's the White Album.</i>

01:13:30.792 --> 01:13:33.056
It's an original first press!

01:13:34.696 --> 01:13:37.790
Is this really for me to keep?

01:13:38.700 --> 01:13:39.724
Yes.

01:13:42.670 --> 01:13:43.728
Thank you.

01:13:44.706 --> 01:13:45.866
Thank you.

01:13:57.819 --> 01:13:59.343
Go get his car.

01:14:03.992 --> 01:14:05.084
You actually read it?

01:14:06.261 --> 01:14:07.250
Brilliant.

01:14:10.165 --> 01:14:12.156
Brilliant? Really?

01:14:14.235 --> 01:14:15.293
Wow.

01:14:17.238 --> 01:14:18.227
Sold.

01:14:21.443 --> 01:14:22.501
Sold?

01:14:22.911 --> 01:14:26.438
<i>Sold? That's $10,000!</i>

01:14:26.514 --> 01:14:29.381
<i>That's $10,000! I love you, man.</i>

01:14:30.785 --> 01:14:32.275
Thank you.

01:14:37.025 --> 01:14:38.686
Yeah.

01:14:38.760 --> 01:14:41.320
<i>I'm gonna take care of that for you
right away, Mr. McCall.</i>

01:14:41.396 --> 01:14:43.023
<i>I'll gas it, too.</i>

01:14:48.102 --> 01:14:50.229
Who's responsible for this?

01:14:52.941 --> 01:14:55.774
<i>You are going to love that,
I guarantee it.</i>

01:14:56.478 --> 01:14:58.207
Yeah? Take a taste.

01:15:07.255 --> 01:15:08.313
I want to ride the roller coaster.

01:15:08.389 --> 01:15:09.413
I want to ride the Ferris wheel.

01:15:09.491 --> 01:15:10.480
I want to ride the roller coaster.

01:15:10.558 --> 01:15:11.547
I want to ride the Ferris wheel.

01:15:11.626 --> 01:15:15.820
- Roller coaster.
- Ferris wheel.

01:15:22.103 --> 01:15:25.368
<i>It's sunny, but it's windy. Should we go?</i>

01:15:25.440 --> 01:15:26.930
You can wear my sweater.

01:15:27.008 --> 01:15:29.568
Is that why you wore a sweater
under your jacket?

01:15:29.644 --> 01:15:31.373
You knew I would say that.

01:15:32.514 --> 01:15:37.645
<i>After 42 years, you're still trying
to get me alone on the beach.</i>

01:15:37.719 --> 01:15:39.084
Maybe. Maybe.

01:16:13.688 --> 01:16:15.952
<i>Raymond, is that you?</i>

01:16:17.191 --> 01:16:19.056
<i>Raymond, is that you?</i>

01:16:20.395 --> 01:16:21.384
Yes.

01:16:24.399 --> 01:16:26.890
<i>Raymond, you finally came.</i>

01:16:28.770 --> 01:16:29.828
Sit!

01:16:31.606 --> 01:16:34.700
<i>Tell me, tell me, what you been doing?</i>

01:16:35.810 --> 01:16:37.437
It's my birthday.

01:16:38.046 --> 01:16:40.139
You want some birthday cake?

01:16:41.516 --> 01:16:42.608
What?

01:16:43.585 --> 01:16:45.348
You can't talk. Your throat.

01:16:45.420 --> 01:16:48.480
<i>Rest then, Raymond.
I have so much to tell you.</i>

01:16:49.190 --> 01:16:51.021
Do you like my room?

01:16:51.225 --> 01:16:53.159
It's so nice.

01:16:55.096 --> 01:16:57.223
I've got all my things here.

01:16:58.533 --> 01:17:00.023
<i>But sometimes,</i>

01:17:01.502 --> 01:17:03.129
I get lonely.

01:17:03.871 --> 01:17:05.964
<i>Raymond, I get so...</i>

01:17:09.711 --> 01:17:13.272
<i>But then, I can always count on Jack.
Jack always comes.</i>

01:17:15.316 --> 01:17:20.117
<i>And he brings me flowers,
helps me, and when we go for walks,</i>

01:17:20.188 --> 01:17:24.181
all the ladies are jealous
because he's so handsome.

01:17:26.060 --> 01:17:28.551
<i>I'm just so proud of him, Raymond.</i>

01:17:29.297 --> 01:17:33.097
<i>See, you missed Jack
grow into the greatest man.</i>

01:17:33.167 --> 01:17:36.068
<i>I mean, he's amazing.
He can do anything.</i>

01:17:36.137 --> 01:17:38.765
<i>I mean, Jack's my only reason to live.</i>

01:17:41.275 --> 01:17:43.641
But he's so angry.

01:17:44.812 --> 01:17:46.677
<i>Mad at you, mad at himself.</i>

01:17:46.748 --> 01:17:52.153
<i>Now, I think he believes
you left because of him.</i>

01:17:52.688 --> 01:17:58.285
<i>He was just a kid,
but he carries that anger every day.</i>

01:17:58.360 --> 01:17:59.884
I wish he'd let it go.

01:18:00.596 --> 01:18:04.191
He'd be much happier if he'd let it all go.

01:18:07.469 --> 01:18:08.697
<i>Raymond,</i>

01:18:10.639 --> 01:18:13.574
you need to tell Jack

01:18:14.877 --> 01:18:16.742
how much you love him.

01:18:18.113 --> 01:18:19.273
We're family.

01:18:20.649 --> 01:18:21.946
Life's

01:18:23.585 --> 01:18:27.077
not worth living without family.

01:18:28.524 --> 01:18:29.513
Right?

01:18:32.995 --> 01:18:34.155
Right?

01:18:42.404 --> 01:18:44.838
Isn't someone going to sing to me?

01:18:49.344 --> 01:18:51.676
<i>I like cake, don't you, Jack?</i>

01:19:02.891 --> 01:19:05.257
<i>Bye, Ma. I love you.</i>

01:20:01.784 --> 01:20:03.513
<i>Hi, Dad.</i>

01:20:05.387 --> 01:20:06.786
- Jack?
- Yeah.

01:20:08.056 --> 01:20:10.115
<i>I'm not Dad. I'm you.</i>

01:20:10.192 --> 01:20:12.023
<i>- I'm Jack, too, you know.
- Are not.</i>

01:20:12.094 --> 01:20:13.584
<i>- Am, too!
- Are not.</i>

01:20:14.396 --> 01:20:17.126
<i>I missed you, Dad.
Where have you been?</i>

01:20:17.199 --> 01:20:19.360
<i>You left and then I saw you a few times,</i>

01:20:20.102 --> 01:20:21.729
but then it was a long time.

01:20:22.137 --> 01:20:24.264
And then you died.

01:20:25.374 --> 01:20:27.137
<i>I'm so sorry, Jack.</i>

01:20:27.209 --> 01:20:29.439
<i>I guess you never know if the last time
you see someone</i>

01:20:30.045 --> 01:20:33.446
is going to be the last time
you ever see someone.

01:20:34.516 --> 01:20:36.711
<i>I wish there was a way
I could make it up to you.</i>

01:20:36.785 --> 01:20:37.774
<i>There is.</i>

01:20:39.021 --> 01:20:41.012
- How?
- Chase me. Come on!

01:21:04.513 --> 01:21:06.105
I forgive you.

01:22:07.843 --> 01:22:09.640
<i>Jack? Jack?</i>

01:22:11.113 --> 01:22:13.513
You're not going to believe this!

01:22:22.124 --> 01:22:26.151
<i>Jack, the tree, it came back to life
and it's incredible! You can talk.</i>

01:22:32.334 --> 01:22:37.135
<i>You've written a beautiful book, Jack.
I'm so proud of you.</i>

01:22:38.240 --> 01:22:41.232
<i>You're hugging me again, Jack.
We spoke about this.</i>

01:22:41.310 --> 01:22:44.609
That's why I'm alive! This is the real me!
That was a fake me that died.

01:22:45.847 --> 01:22:48.509
I just love you so much. Come here.

01:22:48.583 --> 01:22:50.244
- Hello!
- Hello.

01:22:52.421 --> 01:22:53.445
Friends.

01:22:54.623 --> 01:22:56.386
<i>Namaste.</i>

01:22:56.458 --> 01:22:57.618
<i>Welcome to my office,</i>

01:22:57.693 --> 01:23:01.322
the outer manifestation
of my inner being.

01:23:02.698 --> 01:23:03.960
You're both inside me.

01:23:08.270 --> 01:23:11.728
What a beautiful book. What a gift

01:23:11.873 --> 01:23:15.365
<i>to hold, to read, to sell.</i>

01:23:19.514 --> 01:23:21.175
<i>- Hey, Aaron.
- Yes.</i>

01:23:21.717 --> 01:23:23.116
No chanting.

01:23:24.119 --> 01:23:26.451
<i>Of course. Forgive me, wise ones.</i>

01:23:27.756 --> 01:23:30.190
<i>All right, we got three offers here,
three big offers.</i>

01:23:34.096 --> 01:23:35.758
Hey!

01:23:35.832 --> 01:23:36.958
Any of these three would be fine.

01:23:37.033 --> 01:23:40.002
<i>No, no, no, ain't no need to rush,
homey, we got all the leverage here.</i>

01:23:40.503 --> 01:23:42.471
<i>All right, what we have is an opportunity</i>

01:23:42.538 --> 01:23:44.597
to pit all three of these suckas
against each other

01:23:44.674 --> 01:23:46.107
and just grind 'em into the dirt.

01:23:46.409 --> 01:23:50.243
<i>Just take 'em for every last penny
they got, you know, and...</i>

01:23:51.914 --> 01:23:55.077
<i>In an entirely spiritual way, of course.</i>

01:23:55.985 --> 01:23:57.543
<i>You know what, Aaron?
You're the big agent now.</i>

01:23:57.620 --> 01:23:59.713
<i>You got your name on the door.
Why don't you pick, huh?</i>

01:24:01.924 --> 01:24:03.824
May I interest you in a slice of pie?

01:24:03.893 --> 01:24:06.418
<i>I'd love to, but I really have someplace
important I need to be right now.</i>

01:24:06.496 --> 01:24:08.487
What? More important than pie?

01:24:08.564 --> 01:24:11.260
<i>Actually, yes. But give me another hug.</i>

01:24:12.668 --> 01:24:13.999
I love you!

01:24:15.705 --> 01:24:19.402
That's right. I'm the big agent now.
That's my name on the door.

01:24:24.180 --> 01:24:25.511
Steven!

01:24:27.116 --> 01:24:30.279
Why is there a wasabi pea
in my Asian trail mix?

01:24:31.354 --> 01:24:34.323
<i>I am so sorry, Mr. Wiseberger.
I thought I got them all.</i>

01:24:34.390 --> 01:24:36.824
<i>Well, here's one.</i>

01:24:36.893 --> 01:24:38.326
There's a delivery for you.

01:24:38.394 --> 01:24:39.986
<i>Well, bring it in.</i>

01:24:47.203 --> 01:24:49.265
<i>Oh, shit.</i>

01:24:50.073 --> 01:24:51.370
<i>Hold still, let me get this open for you.</i>

01:24:51.441 --> 01:24:52.840
<i>Jack, I don't like surprises.
You know I don't.</i>

01:24:52.909 --> 01:24:53.898
You're gonna like this one.

01:24:53.976 --> 01:24:55.967
You know what happened
the last time I tried to do a surprise...

01:24:56.045 --> 01:24:57.239
- You're gonna like this one.
- What is going on?

01:24:57.313 --> 01:24:58.302
- I'm putting the baby down.
- Okay.

01:24:58.381 --> 01:24:59.814
<i>Okay, all right, okay.</i>

01:24:59.882 --> 01:25:02.248
<i>- Can we please take it off?
- Okay, now, I'll take the blindfold off.</i>

01:25:02.318 --> 01:25:05.310
<i>- Yes, please, take it off.
- Take it off. Okay.</i>

01:25:11.227 --> 01:25:14.321
<i>Jack, this is the house
I've been trying to get you to come see.</i>

01:25:14.397 --> 01:25:16.365
You have to see the inside.

01:25:16.432 --> 01:25:18.297
I've already seen the inside.

01:25:18.367 --> 01:25:20.528
What do you... Why?

01:25:20.603 --> 01:25:22.230
Are you thinking about making an offer?

01:25:22.305 --> 01:25:23.397
Oh, no, I can't.

01:25:23.473 --> 01:25:27.464
- Why not?
- I already own it.

01:25:37.687 --> 01:25:40.520
This is a step in the right direction.

01:25:40.590 --> 01:25:42.679
Yes, but...

01:25:42.725 --> 01:25:45.093
you can't just do this one thing, Jack,

01:25:45.094 --> 01:25:47.028
and think that everything
is gonna be hunky-dory.

01:25:47.096 --> 01:25:49.064
- That's not how it works.
- I hear you.

01:25:49.132 --> 01:25:50.626
You do?

01:25:51.567 --> 01:25:52.829
You hear that?

01:25:52.902 --> 01:25:54.662
What?

01:25:55.571 --> 01:25:57.570
The silence.

01:25:57.874 --> 01:25:59.939
It's quiet.

01:26:00.209 --> 01:26:02.240
I like it.

01:26:03.613 --> 01:26:05.612
Who are you?

01:26:09.252 --> 01:26:10.580
Honey, the tree.

01:26:10.653 --> 01:26:11.950
How did... - Oh, yeah.

01:26:12.021 --> 01:26:15.223
I had Gaudencio carefully
dig it up and next thing you know...

01:26:15.224 --> 01:26:17.750
Boom, it's a tree there.

01:26:17.827 --> 01:26:19.926
Boom. - Boom.

01:26:23.799 --> 01:26:25.967
Boom, boom, boom.

01:26:25.968 --> 01:26:27.369
- Did he say, "Boom"?
- Yes.

